SELECT date_trunc('day', CAST("CalendarDate" AS TIMESTAMP)) AS __timestamp,
      symbol as symbol,
       name AS name,
       max(change_percent_last_day) AS "MAX(change_percent_last_day)"
FROM
  (SELECT c.symbol,
          c.name,
          d.CalendarDate,
          t.time,
          f.price,
          f.market_cap,
          f.change_percent_last_day,
          f.average_1minute
   FROM delta.silver.fact as f
   JOIN delta.silver.dimdate as d ON f.date_id = d.id
   JOIN delta.silver.dimcoin as c ON f.coin_id = c.coin_id
   JOIN delta.silver.dimtime as t ON f.time_id = t.id
   ORDER BY t.time DESC)
   GROUP BY name, symbol,
         date_trunc('day', CAST("CalendarDate" AS TIMESTAMP))
ORDER BY "MAX(change_percent_last_day)" DESC
select coin_id, symbol, name, supply, maxsupply, volume24h, is_current from delta.silver.dimcoin

SELECT    
          c.symbol,
          c.name,
          d.CalendarDate,
          t.Time,
          f.price,
          f.market_cap,
          f.change_percent_last_day,
          f.average_1minute
   FROM delta.silver.fact as f
   JOIN ( 
      select coin_id, symbol, name
      from delta.silver.dimcoin
      where is_current = 'Y'
   ) c ON f.coin_id = c.coin_id
   JOIN delta.silver.dimdate d
   ON d.id = f.date_id
   JOIN delta.silver.dimtime t
   ON t.id =f.time_id
   ORDER BY d.CalendarDate desc , t.Time desc
SELECT count (distinct coin_id) as number from delta.silver.fact
